➜「我和她真只是好朋友」，男人绿茶起来究竟有多婊？
http://www.sohu.com/a/412500436_425113	4522
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p9.itc.cn/images01/20200811/da67ca5de8e441e3bdf888c2064ccd71.gif" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p3.itc.cn/images01/20200811/9bd0ad4ed8e44d20a7169635ecc24bfc.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-center">▼</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">作为史上最无辜饮料</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">天晓得<strong>“绿茶”</strong>犯了什么错</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">鬼使神差地从名词变成形容词</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>一般是指外貌清纯脱俗</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>表面楚楚可怜、岁月静好</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>实则心机满满的女生</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p0.itc.cn/images01/20200811/819b392cf8414ff4baa0449a8b7bc1ae.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>            <div class="lookall-box">
<div class="lookall-shadow"></div>
<section class="lookall">
<a href="javascript:;" class="show-all" id="showMore">
<em>展开全文</em>
</a>
</section>
</div>
<div class="hidden-content control-hide">
<p class="ql-align-center">直到近两年才发现</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">这<strong>“绿茶技艺”</strong>其实跟性别没多大关系</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">不只是女生的专利</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">男生茶起来，同样嘴损心歹</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p8.itc.cn/images01/20200811/4644c6f5d2e84467bb69107cec8a4ff9.png" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-center">今天我们就来聊聊</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>传说中的“绿茶男”</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center">▼</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p3.itc.cn/images01/20200811/35ea41bdbdf148eeb6330cf323e8bc8d.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-center">作为绿茶女的性转版</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">一般长相偏人畜无害</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">介于阳光帅气、奶里奶气之间</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">主要是言语行为令人窒息</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">人前人后两副面孔</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">人前温柔体贴、人畜无害</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">人后工于心计</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p5.itc.cn/images01/20200811/97596bcff60f4653bcdb99bbf8471cc5.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-center">大多打着“好哥们儿”“好朋友”的旗号</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">屡屡越界撩拨于无形</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">一天到晚琢磨着如何撬人墙角</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p1.itc.cn/images01/20200811/1d01f3f83b8e496d85222be6b52d6571.png" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-center">具体婊现在：<strong>嘴甜心细善解人意</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>随叫随到大爱无疆</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>喜欢在日常小事上</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>对别人的女朋友表达心意</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center">什么日常问候</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">“天热别中暑，天冷多添衣</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">来例假时要休息”</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">之类的都是基础操作</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p3.itc.cn/images01/20200811/e83745dbf8fe4ffcb126f1fc2e7bd56b.png" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-center">还特意时刻关注她的屁大小事</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">比如你今天换了头像啊</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">你昨晚发了什么伤春悲秋的文字啊</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">你喜欢的明星出新歌了啊</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">会二十四小时随时准备听你抱怨</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">尤其喜欢听你吐槽伴侣</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">再冷不丁附和两句</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">看似维护实则拉踩</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">瞬间就让正牌男友好感降低</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">你俩的感情就这样慢慢产生了嫌隙</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p4.itc.cn/images01/20200811/b8d34f4828f24112a3d8ec0cff817b4b.png" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"> 以上做法</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">大部分跟温柔体贴的男二人设相符</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">极其容易让女生陷入温柔攻势</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">被挑拨离间了还没发现</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">就这样被迷惑了去</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p1.itc.cn/images01/20200811/9e19b2e4dedc40ee94a2720df892d67b.png" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-center">但他们的目的</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">从来不是取代人家的男友</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">把小姐姐小妹妹搞到手</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">而是<strong>享受整个撩拨的过程</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center">享受撬墙角后的成就感</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">毕竟他们的愿望是</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">好姐姐好妹妹都是我的</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">▼</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p9.itc.cn/images01/20200811/2a4a89cc58d64c8190c5c61018ec6561.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-center">判断一个人是否是绿茶男</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">看他日常说话就能猜个7分</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">那种看似夸赞实则拉踩的</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">有事没事装可怜的</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">基本就可以盖章没跑了</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p7.itc.cn/images01/20200811/1ac3d1cd337d45599de134c1f2794e95.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-center">如果还是不能确定</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">可以看看</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">下面这些经典句式</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>▽</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p2.itc.cn/images01/20200811/8d129db698244f2983f48e7815c899ff.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>▽</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p3.itc.cn/images01/20200811/f4ab99f4e8214e358876afb4dd10e3e4.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>▽</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p8.itc.cn/images01/20200811/812aa92c978a4a448e4a89ead907a6a9.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>▽</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p1.itc.cn/images01/20200811/7b772df49e62433a9dcee3cda910b23e.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>▽</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p6.itc.cn/images01/20200811/b45f1498a41346e881f35d561a5d326d.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>▽</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p9.itc.cn/images01/20200811/0e49b39d58784e08bb54f4dad2767887.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-center">▼</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p8.itc.cn/images01/20200811/c5e1a6cf5aec47459ee89131404d543a.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-center">看了这么多绿茶的特征</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">如果你还对绿茶男没有很好的把握</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">接下来咱们再看看下面这些</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">近两年影视剧中的经典绿茶男形象</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>▽</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p4.itc.cn/images01/20200811/90bfb36735a14c53898fd3efde55922c.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>▽</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p7.itc.cn/images01/20200811/7b64129ef9a04c579faf965a36b96f37.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>
