<p class="ql-align-center">▼</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">前两天刚立了秋</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">小伙伴们大呼：</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">终于要凉快一点了</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">然鹅，热到蒸发的夏天</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">哪那么容易放过你</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">只有玩水才是清凉一夏</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">最正确的打开方式</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">说到“清凉”</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">哪能少得了秘密武器</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">——性感比基尼呢</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">今天文字君就带你们来扒一扒</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">比基尼的“前世今生”</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p8.itc.cn/images01/20200811/29d6e8d28f2c4fd8a51bf0712077456c.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>            <div class="lookall-box">
